---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Sift41" description="How Sift41 curates: no sponsorships, no trends — just evidence, testing, and time.">
  <article class="page">
    <h1 class="abouth1"><span class="t-en">About</span><Logo height={30} /><span class="t-ko">소개</span></h1>

    <h2><span class="t-en">Our Curation</span><span class="t-ko">큐레이션 기준</span></h2>
    <p>
      <span class="t-en"><Logo height={15} /> started with a simple frustration: finding trustworthy recommendations shouldn't be this hard. So we built something different.</span>
      <span class="t-ko"><Logo height={15} />은 '믿을 만한 추천 하나 찾기가 왜 이렇게 힘들지?' 싶은 답답함에서 시작했어요. 그래서 좀 다르게 가보기로 했어요.</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="t-en">We don't accept sponsorships. We don't chase trends. We investigate — comparing evidence, testing real-world performance, and waiting to see what holds up over time. If something doesn't prove itself, it doesn't make the cut. What remains is a curated set of recommendations we stand behind completely.</span>
      <span class="t-ko">협찬 안 받아요. 유행도 안 좇고요. 대신 직접 파봐요 — 근거 비교하고, 실제로 써보고, 시간 지나도 통하는지 끝까지 봐요. 스스로 증명 못 하면 바로 컷이에요. 그렇게 남은 게, 진짜 자신 있게 추천하는 리스트예요.</span>
    </p>

    <h2><span class="t-en">Monthly Edit</span><span class="t-ko">먼슬리 에디트</span></h2>
    <p>
      <span class="t-en">Each month, we spotlight one product we believe in completely — the one we'd tell a friend to buy without hesitation. This is our top pick, updated every month.</span>
      <span class="t-ko">매달 진짜 믿는 제품 딱 하나를 골라 소개해요. 친구한테 '이거 그냥 사' 하는 그 하나요. 매달 새로 바뀌는 톱픽이에요.</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="t-en">We take our time. Every product is researched, tested, and lived with — and only what truly holds up finds a place here. These are the things we'd share with our closest friends.</span>
      <span class="t-ko">절대 안 서둘러요. 다 직접 조사하고, 써보고, 한동안 같이 살아보고 — 진짜 통하는 것만 남겨요. 제일 친한 친구한테나 알려줄 것들이에요.</span>
    </p>

    <p class="note muted">
      <span class="t-en">Transparency note: Some links are affiliate links — we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. This supports our testing and research.</span>
      <span class="t-ko">참고로 일부는 제휴 링크예요. 추가 비용 없이 약간의 수수료가 저희한테 오는데, 이건 테스트하고 리서치하는 데 써요.</span>
    </p>
  </article>
  <style>
    .page { max-width:680px; }
    .abouth1 { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.45rem; }
    .note { margin-top:2rem; font-size:.82rem; border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:1rem; }
  </style>
</Base>
